Iqra\ bi-ismi rabbika alla_th_ee khalaq*a*
Khalaqa al-ins_a_na min AAalaq*in*
Iqra\ warabbuka al-akram*u*
Alla_th_ee AAallama bi*a*lqalam*i*
AAallama al-ins_a_na m_a_ lam yaAAlam
Kall_a_ inna al-ins_a_na laya_t_gh_a_
An ra_a_hu istaghn_a_
Inna il_a_ rabbika a*l*rrujAA_a_
Araayta alla_th_ee yanh_a_
AAabdan i_tha_ _s_all_a_
Araayta in k_a_na AAal_a_ alhud_a_
Aw amara bi*al*ttaqw_a_
Araayta in ka_thth_aba watawall_a_
Alam yaAAlam bi-anna All_a_ha yar_a_
Kall_a_ la-in lam yantahi lanasfaAAan bi*al*nn_as_iya*ti*
N_as_iyatin k_ath_ibatin kh_at_i-a*tin*
FalyadAAu n_a_diyah*u*
SanadAAu a*l*zzab_a_niya*ta*
Kall_a_ l_a_ tu_t_iAAhu wa*o*sjud wa*i*qtarib
